rase was not coined until 1967 by physicist John Wheeler. During the 1930s, such phenomena were typically referred to as \\u0026quot;frozen stars\\u0026quot; or \\u0026quot;collapsed stars\\u0026quot; in theoretical discussions following the work of Karl Schwarzschild.\",\"__typename\":\"Markdown\"},\"isMachineTranslation\":false,\"__typename\":\"MachineTranslatedMarkdown\"},\"__typename\":\"Goof\"},\"__typename\":\"GoofEdge\"}],\"__typename\":\"GoofConnection\"},\"quotesTotal\":{\"total\":6,\"__typename\":\"TitleQuoteConnection\"},\"quotes\":{\"edges\":[{\"node\":{\"displayableArticle\":{\"body\":{\"plaidHtml\":\"\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003ca class=\\\"ipc-md-link ipc-md-link--entity\\\" href=\\\"/name/nm1869101/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu\\\"\\u003eBaroness\\u003c/a\\u003e: Why did you marry him? You are so young and innocent, he\\u0026#39;s like a boiled turnip. There are only two reasons why you marry an older man. Either he\\u0026#39;s rich or, you know, he\\u0026#39;s ... gifted.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\",\"__typename\":\"Markdown\"},\"__typename\":\"DisplayableArticle\"},\"machineTranslatedDisplayableArticle\":{\"body\":{\"language\":{\"id\":\"en-US\"},\"value\":{\"plaidHtml\":\"\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003ca class=\\\"ipc-md-link ipc-md-link--entity\\\" href=\\\"/name/nm1869101/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu\\\"\\u003eBaroness\\u003c/a\\u003e: Why did you marry him? You are so young and innocent, he\\u0026#39;s like a boiled turnip. There are only two reasons why you marry an older man. Either he\\u0026#39;s rich or, you know, he\\u0026#39;s ... gifted.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\",\"__typename\":\"Markdown\"},\"isMachineTranslation\":false,\"__typename\":\"MachineTranslatedMarkdown\"},\"__typename\":\"MachineTranslatedDisplayableArticle\"},\"__typename\":\"TitleQuote\"},\"__typename\":\"TitleQuoteEdge\"}],\"__typename\":\"TitleQuoteConnection\"},\"crazyCredits\":{\"edges\":[],\"__typename\":\"CrazyCreditConnection\"},\"alternateVersions\":{\"tota